<strong>Â Â Â Â  </strong><strong><u>SHORT CUT METHOD-1</u></strong><strong>:-</strong>

Here the focus is on the problem.
<ol>
 	<li>The short cut method summary-</li>
</ol>
<ul>
 	<li>Test your <strong><u>S</u></strong>ubjective <strong><u>U</u></strong>nits of <strong><u>D</u></strong>isturbance<strong>(SUD) </strong>on a scale of 1 â€“ 10 depending on its intensity</li>
 	<li>Set up your affirmation</li>
 	<li>Tap a sequence of 8 points while repeating the remainder phrase</li>
 	<li>Test your SUD again</li>
 	<li>If itâ€™s not zero, then modify your set- up &amp; reminder phrases suitably &amp; repeat steps 2 to 4 until your SUD drops to zero or you are satisfied with your outcome.</li>
</ul>
. Detailed explanation:
<ol>
 	<li><strong>SUD </strong>refers to the value that you assign to your issue on a scale 1-10, this can be done by closing your eyes, deep breathing &amp; focus on the problem, evaluate its intensity &amp; how much you are affected by it 7 assign a number from 1-10</li>
 	<li>Set up affirmation like â€œ<em>Even though I have this</em><em>___________</em> (reminder phrase- your problem), I completely love, forgive &amp; accept myselfâ€</li>
 	<li>Repeat the entire set-up affirmation <strong>3TIMES, </strong><strong>all</strong> the time tapping on your <strong>K</strong>arate <strong>C</strong>hop point (<strong>KC</strong> point)- on the mid metacarpal region on the ulnar side of the palm. You can do this with forefingers of other palm or gently but firmly hitting on the table top without hurting yourself. For remaining point you can use both hands</li>
 	<li>TAPPING SEQUENCE: use your index and middle fingertips, tap gently but firmly 5-7 times on each of this points. Repeat the reminder phrase at each of these points, as you tap.</li>
</ol>
.

